para_trans: The Ministry has decided to reserve the space of the Trimuthi Campus in the main building (ground floor) for various events.
Government Correctional Certificate No. Shakaja-1123 / Q. 7/2023 Niwas-9,
Read: - Government Circular, No. Shakaja-1123 / Q. No. 7/2023/22, D. February 3, 2023.

According to the circular under reference, the Ministry has set certain terms and conditions while reserving the space of the Trimurti Campus at the Main Building, Ground Floor for various events. This Terms and Conditions is being incorporated in serial number 16 as follows.
16) The exhibition / stall / event should not be held for more than 3 days.
This government certificate is available on the website of Fer SAAT www.maharashtra.gov.in a.
